</p><p> “预算将会更大，但也因为我们知道我们即将结束这一章，所以我们都会尽力做到最好。希里安（墨菲）真的很愿意。所以我已经等不及要开始拍摄了。” </p><figure id="attachment_3607734" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3607734" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3607734" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Cillian-Murphy-2-1.jpg" alt="希里安·墨菲" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Cillian-Murphy-2-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Cillian-Murphy-2-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Cillian-Murphy-2-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Cillian-Murphy-2-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Cillian-Murphy-2-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Cillian-Murphy-2-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3607734" class="wp-caption-text"> 《巅峰黑帮》中的希里安·墨菲。图片来源：BBC/Caryn Mandabach Productions Ltd./Robert Viglasky</figcaption></figure><p>最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/barry-keoghan-jokes-hes-going-method-for-peaky-blinders-film-3792228">基奥根谈到了他在即将上映的电影中的角色，称他对加入该系列感到“兴奋又紧张”。</a></p><p>他告诉<a href="https://ew.com/barry-keoghan-talks-joining-peaky-blinders-8709121" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《娱乐周刊》</i></a> <i>：</i> “是的，是的，是的——我等不及了。 [我]是这部剧的超级粉丝，希里安[墨菲]是我的好朋友，我也非常钦佩他作为演员。所以现在就想进入这个领域并了解我的流程——我有一个我正在做的流程，而且我已经很长一段时间没有这样做了，所以我同时感到兴奋和紧张。”</p><p>基奥根继续说道：“刚到片场，那种生锈的感觉又回来了。只是抖掉所有的蜘蛛网。我做了很多促销工作，我一直很放松，我认为人们在发现自己有空闲时间时会感到害怕。</p><p> “我认为有时候作为一名演员和一个人成长是最好的事情，所以我已经度过了这段时光，现在我期待着加入并做一些有创意、有方法的事情。”</p><p>他还承认，在当今时代，继续<i>《浴血黑帮》</i>的发展可能会很困难。 “当时他们没有电话，所以我要关掉电话了，”他开玩笑说。 “得写信了。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-recaps/peaky-blinders-season-6-finale-recap-3196803"><i>《浴血黑帮</i>》第六季也是最后一季</a>将于 2022 年在 BBC One 播出。</p></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/peaky-blinders-movie-update-tim-roth-joins-cast-3797367">《Peaky Blinders》电影更新后：蒂姆·罗斯加入演员阵容</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
穆斯塔法赞扬杜阿·利帕在“Dunya”聆听活动中的激进主义：“作为艺术家，我们有责任举起一面镜子来照见我们的世界” https://www.nme.com/news/music/mustafa-prases-dua-lipas-activism-at-dunya-listening-session-its-our-responsibility-as-artists-to-hold-up-a-镜像到我们的世界-3797303？utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=mustafa-赞美-dua-lipas-activism-at-dunya-listening-session-its-our-responsibility-as-artists-to-hold--我们世界的一面镜子Cordelia LamThu, 26 Sep 2024 14:15:55 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndiePopR&B https://www.nme.com/?p=3797303 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MustafaDua-Lipa-album-listening-session.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Dua Lipa（左）和 Mustafa（右）在舞台上现场表演的两张并排照片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MustafaDua-Lipa-album-listening-session.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MustafaDua-Lipa-album-listening-session-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MustafaDua-Lipa-album-listening-session-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MustafaDua-Lipa-album-listening-session-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MustafaDua-Lipa-album-listening-session-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MustafaDua-Lipa-album-listening-session-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位创作型歌手兼诗人还向 Lipa 谈到了与 Rosalía 合作制作新专辑的“无缝”过程，其中包含来自 The National、Clairo 等人的 Aaron Dessner 的额外贡献</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mustafa-praises-dua-lipas-activism-at-dunya-listening-session-its-our-responsibility-as-artists-to-hold-up-a-mirror-to-our-world-3797303">穆斯塔法 (Mustafa) 赞扬杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 在“Dunya”聆听活动中的积极行动：“作为艺术家，我们有责任为我们的世界举起一面镜子”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MustafaDua-Lipa-album-listening-session.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Dua Lipa（左）和 Mustafa（右）在舞台上现场表演的两张并排照片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MustafaDua-Lipa-album-listening-session.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MustafaDua-Lipa-album-listening-session-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MustafaDua-Lipa-album-listening-session-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MustafaDua-Lipa-album-listening-session-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MustafaDua-Lipa-album-listening-session-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MustafaDua-Lipa-album-listening-session-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨晚（9 月 25 日）<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mustafa">穆斯塔法</a>在杜阿·利帕（Dua Lipa）第二张专辑的聆听环节中赞扬了杜阿·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">利帕（Dua Lipa</a> ）的行动主义，并告诉她“作为艺术家，我们有责任为我们的世界举起一面镜子”。</p><p>这位苏丹裔加拿大歌手兼作曲家和诗人将于明天（9 月 27 日）通过 Jagjaguwar 发行“Dunya”（阿拉伯语的意思是“充满缺陷的世界”）。<a href="https://mustafa.lnk.to/Dunya" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此预订/预保存</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/dua-lipa-live-at-glastonbury-2024-review-setlist-photos-3770003">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 在格拉斯顿伯里 (Glastonbury) 的现场演出：精彩的表演让批评家闭嘴</a></strong></li></ul><p>这部影片是他 2021 年的处女作<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mustafa-announces-debut-record-when-smoke-rises-2911141">《烟雾升起时》</a>的后续作品，该片记录了穆斯塔法长大的多伦多摄政公园暴力社区的生活。他的第一个完整项目荣获 2022 年朱诺奖年度另类专辑奖。</p><p>预计“Dunya”将于本周全面上线，这位音乐家一直在世界各地举办由他的朋友主持的“Kitaba”聆听活动。</p><p>昨天，穆斯塔法在伦敦地球哈克尼剧院与密友利帕发表讲话，分享了对他的穆斯林信仰、他的暴力成长、他为巴勒斯坦和苏丹所做的组织努力以及去年他兄弟的悲惨死亡的深刻个人反思。</p><p>他还演奏了第二张专辑中的全部 12 首曲目，包括单曲“Gaza Is Calling”、“SNL”和“Name Of God”，并公开了与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rosalia">Rosalía</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daniel-caesar">Daniel Caesar</a>在这张密纹唱片上的合作。</p><p>在采访中，穆斯塔法特别赞扬了利帕的友谊和对激进主义的持续承诺。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C9SP4y4RkIg/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.106,71.106 C561.058,72.155 560.06,72.803 558.662,73.347 C557.607,73.757 556.021,7